OL,3,CLive window display encourages
OL,4,Cshoppers to become kidney donors
OL,6,FThree kidney donors will be putting on
OL,7,Fa special shop window display in Kent,
OL,8,Fencouraging people to think about
OL,9,Fbecoming a living donor.
OL,11,FSales shoppers at the Bluewater
OL,12,FShopping Centre in Dartford will get
OL,13,Fmore than they bargained for as,
OL,14,Finstead of buying, they're faced with
OL,15,Fthe question of giving.
OL,17,FThree men who each donated a kidney
OL,18,Fwill stand inside a shop window
OL,19,Falongside six mannequins, representing
OL,20,Fthe six people who die each week in
OL,21,Fthe UK waiting for a kidney.
