OL,6,FEach of the figures are seen lifting
OL,7,Fup their t-shirts to reveal the
OL,8,Fquestion "is it in you to save a
OL,9,Flife?".
OL,11,FThe New Year's campaign launched
OL,12,Ftoday, Friday 3rd January, with Kidney
OL,13,FResearch UK and Give a Kidney.
OL,15,FThe shop facade itself has also been
OL,16,Fgiven a makeover and transformed into
OL,17,Fa giant t-shirt with the window
OL,18,Fdisplaying the shocking statistic.
