OL,6,FShoppers are invited to complete a
OL,7,Fsurvey where people can consider if
OL,8,Fit's inside them to donate a kidney.
OL,10,FThere is also a mirror installed for
OL,11,Fshoppers to use to encourage a brief
OL,12,Fmoment of self reflection on whether
OL,13,Fthey could consider living kidney
OL,14,Fdonation.
OL,16,FAmong the living kidney donors is John
OL,17,FBurns.
