OL,3,CLive window display encourages
OL,4,Cshoppers to become kidney donors
OL,6,FHe said: "In 2017 I read an article in
OL,7,Fa national newspaper about a woman who
OL,8,Fhad given a kidney to someone she
OL,9,Fdidn't know, and it instantly struck a
OL,10,Fchord with me. I did some research
OL,11,Finto the process and after meeting
OL,12,Fkidney recipients at an event and
OL,13,Fhearing directly the impact this had
OL,14,Fon their life, I knew it was something
OL,15,FI had to do."
