OL,3,CLive window display encourages
OL,4,Cshoppers to become kidney donors
OL,6,F"I feel so honoured to be asked to be
OL,7,Fpart of this valuable campaign as I
OL,8,Fknow from personal experience just how
OL,9,Flife changing giving a stranger your
OL,10,Fkidney can be. Most of the good things
OL,11,Fpeople would like to do, they can't
OL,12,Fbecause of other restrictions such as
OL,13,Ffinancial or skill set, but giving a
OL,14,Fkidney, in my opinion, is one of the
OL,15,Fbest long term-good acts someone can
OL,16,Fdo, if they are able."
